negotiator.persistent

Class DefaultPersistentDataContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • negotiator.persistent.DefaultPersistentDataContainer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, PersistentDataContainer

    public class DefaultPersistentDataContainer
extends java.lang.Object
implements PersistentDataContainer
    Default implementation. Just stores the info locally. In fact these containers are not 'persistent' but created every session and then re-loaded with data if applicable.
